info.description: Win cards by spotting identical icons. Player with most cards wins the game.

info.ruleText:
1. Make sure you use some kind of voice chat software.
  2. Every player clicks a seat to join the game.
  3. As soon as you spot the same image on your card and the card in the middle, you say which animal it is and then drag the card to your own pile.
  4. When no cards are left in the middle, the player with the most won cards wins.
